如今巡警更多面对的是“家长里短的琐事”，面对的是“被柴米油盐包裹的普通人”，因此要学会刚柔并济。
Patrolmen now face more "paternalistic trivia" and "ordinary people wrapped up in firewood," so learn to be flexible.
记者 | 应　琛近日，静安区曹家渡派出所的一位年轻民警因其“神仙颜值”登上了网络热搜。
At Ren Chen's recent visit, a young police officer at Cao Jiadu police station in Jingan District boarded the Internet fever search because of his "divine face value."
但这回让他上热搜的却是一名需要送医的男子。
But this time it was a man who needed to be treated.
原来这段在网络热传的视频来自一档叫作《派出所的故事2019》纪实性栏目。
Originally this paragraph in the network heat transmission video from a file called "Story 2019" documentary column.
视频中，一名男子将要被120拉到医院就诊，接警后的曹家渡派出所民警周世奇与同事一起前来查看。
Video, a man will be 120 to be pulled to the hospital, the police after Cao Jiadu police station Zhou Shiqi and colleagues came to check.
该男子看到周世奇出现后，直接就叫周世奇“小唐哥”，称他是大家的“唐僧”，还连连称赞周世奇“真的很帅气”。
The man saw Zhou Shiqi, directly called "little Tang Jie", said he is everyone's "Tang Seng", and repeatedly praised Zhou Shiqi "really handsome.
周世奇接警时的专业与细致，让许多网友印象深刻。
Zhou Shiqi police when the professional and meticulous, let many netizens impressed.
在这档节目中与他一起走红的还有他的搭档兼“师父”马晓亮。
Along with him, his co-star and master, Ma Xiaoliang, made the show a hit.
默契的配合，加上帅气的形象，也让两人成为了网友们心目中超有安全感的“男神”。
The tacit cooperation, together with the handsome image, also let two people become the eyes of the netizens super-safe "male god."
要说周世奇有多少红，记者在朋友圈发了一段“小唐哥”视频后，收到的评论基本上都是“要去采访小唐哥了吗”“这是上海那位有微博超话的警察小哥哥吗”“羡慕~可以不用在曹家渡‘犯罪’就见到本人”……在街面巡逻的周世奇（左一）和马晓亮　沈琳｜摄这不昨天（2月24日），《新民周刊》记者走进了曹家渡派出所，不仅见到了周世奇与马晓亮，还跟着他们做了一次街面巡逻。
If Zhou Shiqi is so popular, the reporter sent a video of "Little Brother" to his friends. "" Is this the little brother of Shanghai policeman who has microblog hyperbole? "" Envy ~ can see me without having to 'commit a crime' in Cao Jiadu.
#千万不要太羡慕嫉妒恨哦#Play11993年出生的周世奇是上海静安公安分局曹家渡派出所的一名民警。
# # Do not envy jealousy and hatred Oh # Play11993 born Zhou Shiqi is a police officer at Cao Jiadu Police Station of the Jingan Public Security Bureau in Shanghai.
说起选择当警察的原因，他坦言是受到了TVB港剧的影响，“里面的阿Sir都很帅，尤其是穿上警察制服的时候”。
Speaking of why he chose to be a policeman, he confessed that he was influenced by the TVB port play, "The Sir inside is very handsome, especially when wearing a police uniform."
再加上，男孩总是有一个想要惩恶扬善的“英雄梦”，因此从高中起，他就立志要成为一名人民警察。
Plus, boys always have a "heroic dream" of trying to punish evil and do good, so from high school on, he aspired to become a people's policeman.
生活中的周世奇2016年从警校毕业的那年，正巧遇上了上海的交通大整治，周世奇先是当了一年的交警。
Life Zhou Shiqi graduated from the police school in 2016, just happened to meet Shanghai's transportation, Zhou Shiqi first became a year of traffic police.
之后，他便来到了曹家渡派出所，被安排在了马晓亮所在的警组，开始了一名巡逻警察的生涯。
After that, he went to Cao Jiadu police station, was placed in Ma Xiaoliang's police team, began a patrol police career.
在周世奇眼中，马晓亮既是“师父”又是“大哥”。
In Zhou Shiqi's eyes, Ma Xiaoliang is both "master" and "elder brother."
“在工作业务上有什么不懂的，我都会向他请教。
"I'll ask him for advice if I don't know anything about my work.
因为兴趣爱好差不多，有些生活上的事情，我也会找马哥商量。
Because the interest hobby is similar, some life matter, I also can consult with the Ma Ge.
”周世奇说，马晓亮就是他的启蒙警长。
Mr. Zhou said Mr. Ma was his first police chief.
刚来曹家渡不久，周世奇就处置过一起棘手的纠纷警情，当时他原本是和另外一名同事前往现场，但马晓亮也主动跟去了。
Shortly after arriving at Cao's Cao Jia Do, Zhou Shiqi handled a thorny dispute with the police, when he and another colleague to the scene, but Ma Xiaoliang also volunteered to follow.
前脚刚踏进小区，周世奇就听到报警人在阳台上高呼“救命”，原来当事双方因为房产闹矛盾，后引发了肢体冲突。
Just before entering the neighborhood, Zhou Shiqi heard the police on the balcony shouted "Help," the original two parties because of property disputes, after the outbreak of physical conflict.
周世奇他们到场后，当事一方情绪更加激动了，当着民警的面就要冲上去打对方。
Zhou Shiqi after their presence, one of the emotions more excited, in front of the police to rush to hit each other.
“当时已经凌晨4点了，但周边邻居都被吵醒在楼道里围观，现场比较混乱而且有人受伤，所以马哥第一时间通知指挥中心联系了医院，后将当事双方隔开后单独谈，因为家事难了，所以马哥一面把法律后果说清楚一面又从处理方法上给建议，待双方冷静下来后，听了有理也就不再闹了。
"It was four o'clock in the morning, but the neighbors were woken up in the hallway, the scene was chaotic and some people were injured. So he first informed the command centre to contact the hospital, separated the two parties and talked to each other separately.
”周世奇　沈琳｜摄从这件事后，周世奇觉得只要有马晓亮在身边，心里就特别有底气，“马哥‘基本功’扎实，平时也很撑我们。
Since then, Zhou Shiqi has felt particularly hearty as long as Ma Xiaoliang is around, "Ma Ge 's basic skills are solid, and usually support us.
有时候听到一些比较复杂的警情时，他都会主动增援过来”。
Sometimes when he hears something more complicated, he comes forward to reinforce him. "
而当问起马晓亮如何评价周世奇时，马哥直呼：“小周同学太优秀了。
And when asked Ma Xiaoliang how to comment on Zhou Shiqi, Ma said straight: "Xiao Zhou classmate is too good.
”在马晓亮眼中，周世奇刚到所里时比较腼腆，在一些处警的过程中碰到比较难缠的人或当事人比较多的情况，会有一点束手束脚，“可能也有一些‘偶像包袱’”。
"In Ma's eyes, Zhou Shiqi was shy when he first arrived at the institute. He met more difficult people or parties in the course of some police work.
但大概仅仅用了一年时间，马晓亮就发现其实已经没有什么东西可以教他了，“周世奇很聪明。
But after only about a year, Ma found that there was nothing left to teach him. Zhou Shiqi was very smart.
现在基本上他在外面巡逻或处警时，有他自己的处置方式，完全能够独当一面。
Now, basically, he has his own way of doing things when he's out patrolling or manning the police, and he can do it all alone.
他也有超越同龄人的成熟和稳重。
He also has the maturity and poise to surpass his peers.
在我有事请假时，我只要稍微关照一下，有他在，我就能很省心”。
When I have to ask for leave of absence, I just give him a little attention. With him, I can be very relieved. "
周世奇参加泥浆越野综合障碍跑当然，私下里的周世奇，和大多数男孩一样，爱打篮球，也爱打游戏，平时也会刷微博和抖音。
Zhou Shiqi takes part in the mud off-road obstacle run, of course, the private Zhou Shiqi, like most boys, love to play basketball, also like to play games, usually also brush micro-blog and chatter.
2周世奇坦言，他并没有想到自己会“再次”走红，“因为电视台拍摄完距离播出已经过了大半年了。
Two weeks Shichi confessed that he did not expect to be "popular" again, "because it has been more than half a year since television filming ended."
其间，我们接警处置了很多案件，说实话早就忘记了这回事了”。
In the meantime, we received police to deal with a lot of cases, to tell the truth has long forgotten this matter.
另一面的周世奇为什么是“再次”？事实上，此前一部《巡逻现场实录2018》已经让周世奇收获迷妹无数。
Why is Zhou Shiqi on the other side "again"? In fact, a previous "on-the-spot video 2018" has let Zhou Shiqi harvest countless fans.
而曹家渡派出所巡逻队更被网友称为“网红巡警天团”。
And Cao Jiadu police station patrol is called "net red patrol police regiment" more netizens.
周世奇劝解走失女孩在片中，他们有人因高颜值“圈粉”，有人因救猫被赞“暖心男神”，也有人爱妻顾家被弹幕“表白”……上海第一代巡警姜慧而说起他们的师父，更是大名鼎鼎的上海第一代巡警姜慧。
Zhou Shiqi persuades lost girls in the film, they are high-value "circle powder", someone was praised for saving the cat "warm-hearted male God," others love his wife and his family was "Shooting the Shooting"... Shanghai first generation patrol officer Jiang Hui told of their master, is the famous Shanghai first generation patrol officer Jiang Hui.
要知道姜慧出名的时候，社交媒体还没有像现在这么发达，而网上已经有不少他的“传说”，人送名号“马路神探”，名副其实的“初代网红”。
You know, when Jiang Hui was famous, social media was not as developed as it is now, and there are a lot of his "legends" on the Internet, people give the name "road detective," a veritable "first generation net red.
毒贩、持械歹徒、爆炸物……在姜慧26年的巡逻生涯中都曾遇到。
Drug dealers, armed gangsters, explosives... all encountered Jiang throughout his 26-year patrol career.
“传帮带”是曹家渡派出所历来的优良传统，如今已是副所长的姜慧将接力棒传到了马晓亮、周世奇的手中。
"Mentorship band" is the Cao Jiadu police station has always had a fine tradition, such as now deputy director Jiang Hui will pass the baton to Ma Xiaoliang, Zhou Shiqi hands.
在姜慧看来，如今巡警更多面对的是“家长里短的琐事”，面对的是“被柴米油盐包裹的普通人”，因此要学会刚柔并济。
In Jiang's view, police patrols today face more "paternalistic trivia" and "ordinary people wrapped up in firewood and salt," so learn to be flexible.
3目前正处于新冠肺炎疫情防控时期，周世奇告诉记者，疫情期间出现了不少新的警情。
At present is in the period of New Crown Pneumonia prevention and control, Zhou Shiqi told reporters that during the outbreak of a number of new police.
周世奇处警中2月初的某个夜班，周世奇和马晓亮就接到有人报警称，辖区内某家酒吧存在噪声扰民的情况。
Zhou Shiqi police in early February a night shift, Zhou Shiqi and Ma Xiaoliang have been reported to a bar in the area of noise disturbing people.
当时已经是凌晨3点多，两人迅速到达现场，发现酒吧确实存在营业行为。
It was about 3 a. m., and the two men arrived quickly to find out that the bar was indeed doing business.
“按照相关规定，例如酒吧等一些娱乐性场所那个时候还不能营业。
"Some entertainment venues, such as bars, were closed for business at the time," he said.
”周世奇表示，当时酒吧内大约有30人在喝酒聊天，基本上没有戴口罩，“尤其在疫情期间，这样的行为特别危险。
About 30 people in the bar were drinking and talking, mostly without face masks, "which is particularly dangerous during the outbreak," Zhou said.
但酒吧内的客人大多是外国人，可能也不太了解目前防疫的一些规定”。
But most of the guests in the bar are foreigners and probably don't know much about current vaccination regulations.
周世奇和马晓亮先对顾客进行了相关的告知并做了清场，又责令酒吧立即停止营业。
Zhou Shiqi and Ma Xiaoliang first to the customer of the relevant information and do the clearing, and ordered the bar to stop business immediately.
后来，他们又联系到酒吧的负责人，对他进行了教育，以及后续的处理。
Later, they contacted the head of the bar to educate him and follow up.
此外，因为外来人员小区不让进、外卖不让进、快递不让进等情况产生的纠纷也时有发生；还比如，重点地区返沪人员被拦在小区门口被要求隔离的情况也很多，这时也需要民警到场维持秩序。
In addition, disputes have arisen over the denial of entry and take-out to foreign communities and the denial of express deliveries, as well as the large number of cases of people returning to Shanghai from key areas being asked to be quarantined at the gates of the district, which also requires the presence of civilian police to maintain order.
“我们还碰到过，宾馆出于安全考虑不让一些外地来的人员入住，但这是一个老百姓的正常需求，我们肯定要保证的，所以要帮他们解决晚上住哪里。
"We've come across people from outside the hotel who are not allowed to stay because of security concerns, but this is a normal need of the general population, and we certainly want to make sure that we help them out at night.
”周世奇说，他之前还在抖音上看到一个顾客因为进店买东西没戴口罩，店员拒绝卖给他，双方产生纠纷以后报警的短片，“民警到场后的处置方法，我觉得也是我们工作上可以学习的”。
Zhou Shiqi said he had seen a customer walk into the store without a mask and the clerk refused to sell it to him. There were short clips of calls to the police after the dispute.
曾经“抓坏人”是人们对警察这一职业最朴素的认知，而电视剧里的“大场面”也是周世奇的心之所向，但真正工作后，周世奇说，他更希望这样的“大场面”还是不要出现的好。
Once, "catching bad guys" was the simplest recognition of the police profession, and the "big picture" in the TV series was what Zhou Shiqi was looking for, but after the actual work, Zhou said he would have preferred such a "grand spectacle" not to occur.
马晓亮与周世奇（右一）在街面巡逻　沈琳｜摄当天的巡逻过程中，周世奇发现，街上的行人明显多于之前。
Xiao Liang Ma and Zhou Shiqi (first from the right) patrol the streets less than before, less than usual, Zhou Shiqi found.
他也提醒道：“疫情期间，希望广大市民可以减少出门，减少聚会，勤洗手，出门务必戴口罩，一起坚持到疫情结束，全民共同做好疫情的防控工作。
"During the epidemic, we hope that the general public can reduce their travel, reduce gatherings, wash their hands frequently, wear masks outside the home, and stay together until the end of the epidemic," he warned.
”征集令《新民周刊》现面向全国征集新冠肺炎采访对象和真实故事：如果你是参与抗击新冠肺炎疫情的医护人员或其家属，我们希望聆听你的“战疫”故事，也希望传达你的诉求。
The Call for New People is now soliciting interviews and true stories from around the country: If you are a healthcare worker or family member involved in the fight against pneumonia, we hope to hear your "plague" story and convey your message.
如果你是确诊、疑似患者本人或家属，我们希望了解你和家人如何“抗疫”的过程，让外界了解你的真实经历。
If you are a confirmed, suspected patient or family member, we would like to know how you and your family have responded to the epidemic and let the outside world know about your true experience.
如果你是疫情严重地区的普通市民，我们希望展现你的乐观，并倾听你所需的帮助。
If you are an ordinary citizen of a highly affected area, we hope to show your optimism and listen to the help you need.
如果你是公共服务人员或各类捐助者，我们希望看到你的“最美逆行”，记录下你的无私。
If you are a public service provider or a variety of donors, we want to see your "most beautiful retrograde" and record your selflessness.
……抗击新冠肺炎疫情，我们诚征对疫情了解的社会各界人士，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
To fight the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic, we sincerely invite all sectors of the community to understand the epidemic, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
